    title: "密码学",
    description: "古典密码、现代密码、哈希碰撞、侧信道攻击等密码学挑战。",
    link: "/docs/crypto-classical",
    status: "在线",
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-8"><path d="M18 8h-1V6c0-2.76-2.24-5-5-5S7 3.24 7 6v2H6c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v10c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V10c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm-6 9c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2s.9-2 2-2 2 .9 2 2-.9 2-2 2zm3.1-9H8.9V6c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1 1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1v2z"></path></svg>`,
  },
  {
    title: "PWN",
    description: "栈溢出、堆利用、ROP、格式化字符串等二进制漏洞利用技术。",
    link: "/docs/pwn-stack-overflow",
    status: "在线",
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-8"><path d="M19.14 12.94c.04-.3.06-.61.06-.94 0-.32-.02-.64-.07-.94l2.03-1.58c.18-.14.23-.41.12-.61l-1.92-3.32c-.12-.22-.37-.29-.59-.22l-2.39.96c-.5-.38-1.03-.7-1.62-.94l-.36-2.54c-.04-.24-.24-.41-.48-.41h-3.84c-.24 0-.43.17-.47.41l-.36 2.54c-.59.24-1.13.57-1.62.94l-2.39-.96c-.22-.08-.47 0-.59.22L2.74 8.87c-.12.21-.08.47.12.61l2.03 1.58c-.05.3-.07.62-.07.94s.02.64.07.94l-2.03 1.58c-.18.14-.23.41-.12.61l1.92 3.32c.12.22.37.29.59.22l2.39-.96c.5.38 1.03.7 1.62.94l.36 2.54c.05.24.24.41.48.41h3.84c.24 0 .44-.17.47-.41l.36-2.54c.59-.24 1.13-.56 1.62-.94l2.39.96c.22.08.47 0 .59-.22l1.92-3.32c.12-.22.07-.47-.12-.61l-2.01-1.58zM12 15.6c-1.98 0-3.6-1.62-3.6-3.6s1.62-3.6 3.6-3.6 3.6 1.62 3.6 3.6-1.62 3.6-3.6 3.6z"></path></svg>`,
  },
  {
    title: "杂项",
    description: "隐写术、取证分析、流量分析、编码解码等综合技能挑战。",
    link: "/docs/misc-steganography",
    status: "在线",
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-8"><path d="M21 3H3c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h18c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 16H3V5h18v14zM5 15h14v3H5z"></path></svg>`,
  },
  {
    title: "移动安全",
    description: "Android/iOS 逆向、动态分析、脱机破解等移动端安全研究。",
    link: "/docs/mobile-android",
    status: "在线",
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="size-8"><path d="M17 1.01L7 1c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v18c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h10c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V3c0-1.1-.9-1.99-2-1.99zM17 19H7V5h10v14z"></path></svg>`,
  },
